location.fullValue: Monarch Country Club At Martin Downs

data.description: Lake front! 24-hour guard-gated DiVosta community with a spectacular water feature entrance. This exceptional lakefront 2 bedroom 2.5 bath home has a new metal roof installed in 2018, It's in immaculate condition and was chosen for its location offering privacy and excellent views down the entire shimmering lake. Lots of wide sidewalks for walking and enjoying the tree-lined streets on your way to the oversized resort-style pool lined with palm trees and chaise lounges, creating a perfect oasis for relaxation and leisure. There is also tennis, pickleball, bocce ball, and a new playground in 2023! The home has newer appliances, large walk-in closet in master bedroom also with beautiful views of the lake. HOA includes High-Speed Internet and ground maintenance. This is a must-see proper
